@SecPompeo @DeptofDefense @realDonaldTrump When I see your image on #FoxPropagandaNetwork #TrumpTV it conjures up images of Red China and the USSR propaganda networks from the 60’s. So, why are you hating on China now. Distractions from  #coronavirus ? #GeorgeFloyd or the #2020Election in general?
